item.title: Tensorflow the Confusing Parts 1
item.description: Tensorflow for ML Researchers: The Confusing Parts Click here to skip the intro and dive right in What is this? Who are you? I’m Jacob, a Google AI Resident. When I started the residency program in the summer of 2017, I had a lot of experience programming, and a good understanding of machine learning, but I had never used Tensorflow before. I figured that given my background I’d be able to pick it up quickly.
